哪怕以前相处的很融洽，也只是朋友间正常的交往呀…为什么其他同学（可能也包括他）会觉得我不负责任呢?我知道女生如果对和自己表白的男生不拒绝、又没有明确的回应是不对的，但前提是他从未和我表白过，从未说过“我喜欢你”之类的呀?"},"attached_info":"Cj8I2tSRhK+3tuUHEAMaCDMyMTAxMTAwINuG5eMFMAI4hQFAEXIJMzE0MjExMjE2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"137 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-addcd48666de50b92afb0881b36f8309_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"18_1622889393.8166912","card_id":"Q_462472612","target":{"id":462472612,"title":"2021年618活动  AirPods Pro 值得购买吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/462472612","type":"question","created":1622470923,"answer_count":55,"follower_count":116,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[221195,401924,546691,720998],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4I2tSRhK+3tuUHEAMaCDY1MDUxMDc4IIvi04UGMAA4dEAScgk0NjI0NzI2MTJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"99 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-2677dfe92c7e725caf8d5c9d6b34537e_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"19_1622889393.8171573","card_id":"Q_454175132","target":{"id":454175132,"title":"最近书荒有什么好的小说推荐？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/454175132","type":"question","created":1618191655,"answer_count":46,"follower_count":159,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[73,1873,15858,32280,33450],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I2tSRhK+3tuUHEAMaCDYzMjA3NDM2IKfKzoMGMAA4nwFAE3IJNDU0MTc1MTMyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"80 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-fb5e19dc6502965a0d2524f2966ab2d6_b.jpg"}]},{"